{"tid":1415082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暴動可判因十年,但「縱火」可判終身監禁","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:33:26.000Z","uid":134071,"like":17,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bcce3279587b2823a10ca04de265dacadfd47ce4","tid":1415082,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:11:29.000Z","msg":"一時「縱火」或「嚴重傷人」, 或者好hi, 但打擊不到中共當權人士, 而且可能被判終身監禁, 大家小心為上. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160210/19485831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160210%2F19485831&d=m%2FvCTr80Ma3Q2SiS6jp77a%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=224aab44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160210%2F19485831&h=e7a210a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160210/19485831</a><br />\n<br />\n//資深大律師湯家驊指示威者若單是磚擲傷人此行為，已可能觸犯《侵害人身罪條例》第17條意圖造成身體嚴重傷害而傷人罪，這罪名與縱火罪名一樣是可判終身監禁的重罪。另據《公安條例》第19條暴動罪，若有3人或以上在公眾地方非法集結，並破壞社會安寧（如作出暴力行為使他人感到恐慌），有份參與集結的人即可能屬集結暴動，最高可判監10年。//"},{"pid":"69772725b35b8e5b881dd62fc0c1eac7fcb60f91","tid":1415082,"uid":54303,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:12:21.000Z","msg":"又點？香港本來都無希望架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以今次要贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2efcbb4b6aa5f7e08ac1fe206720213af954c0","tid":1415082,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:13:00.000Z","msg":"大家小心<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1659418/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1659418%2F&d=m%2FvCTr80Ma3Q2SiS6jp77a%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=80b136e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1659418/</a><br />\n<br />\n13年前金鐘縱火14人傷 6旬翁判囚終生<br />\n社會 21:58 2017/02/10 <br />\n<br />\n港鐵發生懷疑掟汽油彈縱火案，最少12人受傷。港鐵自1979年通車以來，2004年發生首宗縱火案，一名精神有問題的6旬翁趁早上繁忙時間，在一列載著1200名上班族的列車上縱火，14人輕傷。兇徒其後被判終身監禁。"},{"pid":"fb328f7f0ccf94bfb4fc0a5195ee53052e78f227","tid":1415082,"uid":52041,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"施君龍好似放火燒死左個入境，最後有咩後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec80a96fa86a26856dea46fb9645605c5affbc0","tid":1415082,"uid":245484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:14:58.000Z","msg":"冇人叫你放完企係到比人捉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bed92a8abcb9ea782bf72becce9f6cfdfcb16c4","tid":1415082,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb328f7f0ccf94bfb4fc0a5195ee53052e78f227","tid":1415082,"uid":52041,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"施君龍好似放火燒死左個入境，最後有咩後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:15:03.000Z","msg":"人地有中共幫<br />\n<br />\n示威者無"},{"pid":"ef953436f800586a15a8d20f4b7f4a1c01d3b7e5","tid":1415082,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"69772725b35b8e5b881dd62fc0c1eac7fcb60f91","tid":1415082,"uid":54303,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:12:21.000Z","msg":"又點？香港本來都無希望架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以今次要贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:16:25.000Z","msg":"梁天琦都話依過係長期戰, 保住有用之身最重要<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦: &quot;香港革命&quot;可能需要16年的時間, 才會成功<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377586/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377586/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"8412ec181a650c2e9f567c0edac8e63350bc3497","tid":1415082,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:17:09.000Z","msg":"呢場輸咗，思想控制再教育，社會評分系統，軟禁你香港一世，火車地鐵都冇得坐，行路上班過人生。"},{"pid":"863e5f78fcf89bf2bd2bcdfc52e4400cce460c20","tid":1